**修正后的快速排序代码：**

```python
def quicksort(arr):
 if len(arr) <= 1:
 return arr
[4C
 pivot = arr[0]
 
 left = [num for num in arr[1:] if num < pivot]
 right = [num for num in arr[1:] if num >= pivot]
 
 return quicksort(left) + quicksort(right)

# 测试示例
print(quicksort([3,6,8,10,1,2,1]))
```

**斐波那契数列第20项的计算过程：**

斐波那契数列是从0和1开始，每个后续数字为前两个数字之和。具体计算如下：

- F(0) = 0 
- F(1) = 1 
- F(2) = F(0)+F(1)=1 
- F(3) = F(1)+F(2)=2 
- F(4) = F(2)+F(3)=3 
- F(5) = F(3)+F(4)=5 
- F(6) = F(4)+F(5)=8 
- F(7) = F(5)+F(6)=13 
- F(8) = F(6)+F(7)=21 
- F(9) = F(7)+F(8)=34 
- F(10) = F(8)+F(9)=55 
- F(11) = F(9)+F(10)=89 
- F(12) = F(10)+F(11)=144 
- F(13) = F(11)+F(12)=233 
- F(14) = F(12)+F(13)=377 
- F(15) = F(13)+F(14)=610 
- F(16) = F(14)+F(15)=987 
- F(17) = F(15)+F(16)=1597 
- F(18) = F(16)+F(17)=2584 
- F(19) = F(17)+F(18)=4181 
- F(20) = F(18)+F(19)=6765 

